{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The first test run exposed two real cleanup issues rather than a design problem: RTL wasn\u2019t cleaning the DOM between cases in this setup, and the offline-path warning was polluting test output. I\u2019m tightening the test harness and the dev...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_56", "text": "The first test run exposed two real cleanup issues rather than a design problem: RTL wasn\u2019t cleaning the DOM between cases in this setup, and the offline-path warning was polluting test output. I\u2019m tightening the test harness and the dev-only logging guard now, then I\u2019ll rerun the full frontend verification loop.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 109, "prompt_index": 3, "prompt_name": "02 \u2014 Scaffold the React Frontend with Vite", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-03-31T21:16:00-07:00"}
